messages.content:
Extract the first name and the last name from the following full name. The first name may contain one or more words, and the last name is the final word in the full name. Provide the result in JSON format.

Input:
Anna Maria Smith

Output:
{
  "first_name": "Anna Maria",
  "last_name": "Smith"
}

Input:
James A. Johnson

{
  "first_name": "James A.",
  "last_name": "Johnson"
}

Input:
Mary-Jane O'Reilly

{
  "first_name": "Mary-Jane",
  "last_name": "O'Reilly"
}
